HEADWORD: Drencher
<hw>Drench"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who,
or that which, west or steeps.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who administers a drench.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Drengage</ent>⟦br⟧
